@startuml seq_05_change_settings
title Sequence Diagram: UC-05 Change Settings

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "User Controller" as Controller
participant "User Service" as Service
participant "User Repository" as Repo

User -> Frontend: Open Settings page
Frontend -> Controller: GET /api/users/settings
Controller -> Service: Get Settings
Service -> Repo: Find User Settings by ID
Repo --> Service: Current Settings
Service --> Controller: Current Settings
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK (Settings data)
Frontend --> User: Display Settings Form

User -> Frontend: Modify settings & Save
Frontend -> Controller: PUT /api/users/settings {new_settings}
Controller -> Service: Update Settings
Service -> Service: Validate settings values
Service -> Repo: Update User Settings
Repo --> Service: Settings updated
Service --> Controller: Updated Settings
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Show success message
@enduml